{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>李家鼎（鼎爺）前妻施明的喪禮將於今日（4月22日）於大圍寶福紀念館設靈，翌日大殮儀式結束後，靈柩隨即奉移富山火化場火化。李泳豪與父親李家鼎以及太太Agnes於下午4時左右抵達寶福紀念館，三人看見傳媒時有停低給大家拍照，鼎爺明顯暴瘦了很多，問到鼎爺瘦了很多？他沒有回答，三人未有接受訪問便步到靈堂，可是門外有工作人員攔住了他們，並不讓Agnes進靈堂內，她需要在靈堂外等候。問到Agnes不准她入內可會開心？預了無得入都來？有什麼說話想同奶奶講？同奶奶關係是否不好？她都沒有回答。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657508301312000192506.jpeg/6tx0n06_Ydo1c7GT4SMuhrXOiYWWi7nZSyaynX0msp0\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657522709270528143978.jpeg/WLVvVW6WJvqYyFK3B1PfKK16mtnoL2Ph3qcyueinMrk\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657520045756416254683.jpeg/Wv6yTMbfIsn5SsE0kE9Aq8PQ8QTFfcpH-iq9B8wqvQc\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657517298356224618493.jpeg/y7bsGgFm5H1nodpSypgLDi1Wc6SREGgu9L3tlcK97ZU\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657514408349696427601.jpeg/EIlESk8Id86xT9PWTjU1Yi8Ovli7Txzq8pW49cSVuPU\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123657511447040000645318.jpeg/CXtMczHpd6aCtPxBEvN5BMKAVkor_Fr-r0IuP5lCLj8\" alt=\"（葉志明攝）\"><figcaption>（葉志明攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T08:45:51.468921+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":281,"images":6,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}